comments:
The following code causes the parser to silently fail:

helper context UML2!"uml::Element" def : myOclType : OclType =
	let type : OclType = self->oclType()
	in if type = UML2!"uml::DataType"
	   then UML2!"uml::Classifier"
	   else type endif;

The entire ATL library can be found here:

http://ssel.vub.ac.be/viewvc/PlatformKit/platformkit-java/transformations/UML2Comparison.atl?revision=7375&view=markup

Got a stack trace:
